While perform a bulk operation, on the third screen, there is a checkbox for sending notifications for the bulk operation:
{quote}
[ ] Send mail for this update
_By selecting this option, an update notification will be sent for each issue affected by this bulk operation_
{quote}

This description is not clear for the end-users and it should convey a clearer message about who will receive such notifications.

*Suggestion*
Include the text below:
{quote}
[ ] Send mail for this update
_By selecting this option, an update notification will be sent for each issue affected by this bulk operation._ *The notification will be sent according to each issue's notification scheme for the selected operation.*
{quote}

